{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"storage","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Window/storage_event","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>当存储区域（localStorage 或 sessionStorage）被修改时，将触发 storage 事件。查看 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Web_Storage_API\">Web Storage API</a> 来获取更多信息。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"常规信息","title":"常规信息","isH3":false,"content":"<p>说明：<em><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/webstorage/#the-storage-event\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Web Storage</a></em></p>\n<table class=\"properties\">\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <th scope=\"row\">接口</th>\n      <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/StorageEvent\"><code>StorageEvent</code></a></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <th scope=\"row\">是否冒泡</th>\n      <td>No</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <th scope=\"row\">目标</th>\n      <td>DefaultView (<code>&lt;window&gt;</code>)</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <th scope=\"row\">默认行为</th>\n      <td>无</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"属性","title":"属性","isH3":false,"content":"<table>\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th>Property</th>\n      <th>Type</th>\n      <th>Description</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td><code>target</code> <span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></td>\n      <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></td>\n      <td>事件目标 (DOM 树中的最大目标)</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><code>type</code> <span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></td>\n      <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String\"><code>DOMString</code></a></td>\n      <td>事件的类型</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><code>bubbles</code> <span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></td>\n      <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Boolean\"><code>Boolean</code></a></td>\n      <td>事件通常是否会出现冒泡</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><code>cancelable</code> <span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></td>\n      <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Boolean\"><code>Boolean</code></a></td>\n      <td>事件是否可取消</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><code>key</code> <span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></td>\n      <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String\"><code>DOMString</code></a> (string)</td>\n      <td>键更改时</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><code>oldValue</code> <span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></td>\n      <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String\"><code>DOMString</code></a> (string)</td>\n      <td>正在更改键的旧值</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><code>newValue</code> <span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></td>\n      <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String\"><code>DOMString</code></a> (string)</td>\n      <td>正在更改键的新值</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><code>url</code> <span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></td>\n      <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String\"><code>DOMString</code></a> (string)</td>\n      <td>键更改的文档的地址</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><code>storageArea</code> <span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></td>\n      <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Storage\"><code>Storage</code></a></td>\n      <td>受影响的存储对象</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范","id":"规范","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/indices.html#event-storage","title":"HTML Standard"}],"query":"api.Window.storage_event"}}],"toc":[{"text":"常规信息","id":"常规信息"},{"text":